##Import the FAS Litters CSV 

Import the dataset and clean the names
```{r}
litters_df= read_csv("data_import_examples/FAS_litters.csv")
view(litters_df)

names(litters_df)

litters_df = janitor::clean_names(litters_df)
names(litters_df)
```
